>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nIf a courier arrives at your address and is unable to deliver on the arranged delivery date because you are not there, refuse to sign or you refuse delivery you will be liable for the cost of any re-delivery charge when applicable. All deliveries must be signed for.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nDeliveries cannot be left outside in porches, garages or any other location or with any third party.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nDeliveries cannot be made to any third party or alternative delivery address and must be made to the registered address of the cardholder.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="ques">\r\nWhen Your Order Arrives\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nWhen your order arrives, you want to be sure the quantities match what you ordered.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nTo guarantee customer satisfaction, please make note of the following when receiving your order:\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nVisually inspect the condition and entirety of your delivery, make sure to note missing items or damaged materials. The order confirmation you receive lists all the materials and quantities you ordered. You will need to examine the delivery and count each item to make sure everything ordered has been received.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nDO NOT let the driver leave until you have verified the material received is in good \r\ncondition and that all material has been accounted for.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nEvery effort is made to ensure that your goods are delivered in perfect condition. Please inspect your goods immediately on delivery as no claims with regard to damaged items can be made after our driver has left the delivery address, unless signed for as damaged on delivery.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nIn the unlikely event that some of your goods are damaged we will collect and replace the product. Damaged or faulty goods must be reported to us within 48 hours of delivery either by phone: 01625 582111, fax: 01625 582424 or email: SALES@FLOORSANDUK.COM, preferably whilst the delivery driver is still there. Any damaged goods MUST be signed as damaged on the delivery note. We will then make further arrangements with you to replace the damaged goods (please see our Returns Policy).\r\n<br /><br >\r\nNo liability can be accepted for costs caused by late deliveries or for any other reason.\r\nTherefore we advise against booking for installations until goods have been received. \r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="ques">\r\nConsumer Rights\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nNone of the above Terms and Conditions affect your statutory consumer rights. \r\n</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="ques">\r\nCompany Information & Contact Us\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="fontsize18">\r\nFloorSand UK Limited, which is a company incorporated in England and Wales, registered under company number 07064910, and whose registered office is at:<br /><br />\r\n132 Great Ancoats Street<br />\r\nManchester<br />\r\nM4 6DE<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Telephone Numbers:</strong><br />\r\n01625 582111 Main Office Enquiries<br />\r\n01625 582567 Floor Sanding Material Supplies<br />\r\n0161 798 0888 Accounts <br />\r\n<br />\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:info@floorsanduk.com">INFO@FLOORSANDUK.COM</a><br />\r\nWebsite: <a href="http://floorsanduk.com">www.floorsanduk.com</a>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>', 'simple', '', 'off', 1367156330, 1367145576),
